Description: Time and weather announcement system for AllStar
 This package provides scripts for announcing time and weather conditions
 over AllStar nodes. It includes:
 .
 The package includes:
  * saytime.pl - Script to announce current time
  * weather.pl - Script to announce weather conditions
  * Sound files for time and weather announcements
 .
 Features:
  * Automatic time announcements
  * Current weather conditions
  * Support for ZIP codes and airport codes
  * Weather Underground API support for international airport codes
  * Configurable weather data source selection
  * Caching for improved performance
  * Custom sound directory support
  * Comprehensive logging 